d-throw-object-at-her-3497318">向舞台投掷物体的粉丝发生冲突</a>。</p><p>其他受到这一危险趋势影响的艺术家包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/harry-styles-penis-hit-by-flying-object-during-chicago-concert-3330933">Harry Styles</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lil-nas-x-pauses-gig-after-fan-throws-sex-toy-on-stage-3464509">Lil Nas X</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/drake-hits-out-at-fan-for-throwing-book-at-his-head-onstage-3485633">Drake</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/cardi-b-throws-microphone-at-audience-member-who-chucked-drink-at-her-on-stage-3475213">Cardi B</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pink-stunned-as-fan-throws-mothers-ashes-onto-stage-at-bst-hyde-park-3461977">Pink</a> 。</p><p>最令人担忧的案例是，在纽约演出<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bebe-rexha-collapses-on-stage-after-being-struck-in-head-by-fans-phone-at-gig-3457928">期间，一名观众将手机扔到</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bebe-rexha">贝比·雷克萨 (Bebe Rehxa)</a>的脸上<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bebe-rexha-attacker-reportedly-threw-phone-at-her-head-because-it-would-be-funny-3458236">，因为他认为这会“有趣”，导致她</a>需要缝针。</p><p>许多粉丝和现场表演者谴责那些造成这种破坏的人。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/adele-calls-on-fans-to-stop-throwing-things-at-artists-on-stage-3464740">阿黛尔在 7 月份的一场拉斯维加斯演出中呼吁音乐会观众“停止扔东西”</a> ，并警告说：“我他妈的敢于向我扔东西，我他妈的会杀了你。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billie-eilish-says-fans-throwing-objects-at-performers-is-infuriating-3468291">比莉·艾利什 (Billie Eilish)</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/corey-taylor-on-fans-throwing-things-at-performers-artists-arent-regarded-as-people-anymore-3479191">科里·泰勒 (Corey Taylor)</a>和凯莉·克拉克森 ( <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kelly-clarkson-warns-fans-against-throwing-things-onstage-at-las-vegas-residency-3476190">Kelly Clarkson)</a>等人也公开反对在舞台上扔东西的趋势。 “当你在上面时，这绝对令人愤怒，”艾利什说。 “你处于弱势地位。”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/death-grips-cut-short-us-concert-after-getting-hit-by-glowsticks-3515333">《Death G